eamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501410/extras/bb5ff7e6bbd9843ee590f89dbb47be11.mp4?t=1641863057\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Face bosses in epic battles!</strong> You must deal with wicked bosses who will challenge all your strengths and tactics. But be careful: as the levels are randomly generated, you can find the bosses' doors right away. Have the wisdom to know your limits and the perception of the right time to face them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501410/extras/de9f0d3dda73aaa4762271f15c79e093.poster.avif?t=1641863057\" width=622 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501410/extras/de9f0d3dda73aaa4762271f15c79e093.webm?t=1641863057\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1501410/extras/de9f0d3dda73aaa4762271f15c79e093.mp4?t=1641863057\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Achieve immortality!</strong> Help Gallar to continue his long and glorious journey into eternity. Will you be able to fight until the end for the lost relic?</li></ul>",
